I made an avs script to crop, resize & sharpen.

After encoding, i watched it on a 52inch TV,
its prety good, deffinatley watchable.
The black box in the corner is annoying but you get use to it.
The colors are off, i tried my best but there still not great.
The DVD is due on the 28th March.
Download the sample first to check that your happy with the quality.
